snippet.title: Time Is Honey // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2140570/Time_Is_Honey/

Time Is Honey is a relaxing idle game where you open packs to discover a variety of unique bees. Take care of them in real-time and then turn it all into profit. Unlock and customize all of the unique hives and enjoy completing your collection of bees.

Developed by
quickdog
